snippet.title: Ultimate Trial : Release Trailer
snippet.description:
If you notice any issue or have any feedback or suggestion, feel free to let us know on our Discord Server !
The patch will be also available in this server.

Discord : https://discord.gg/bSxVK8xSHu

Download : https://github.com/RichieUltimate/ultimate-trial

OST : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLYk0419DovZIqIPCqFXclkKI8gfu2PJ_X

How to fix the crash in PJ64 : https://youtu.be/IX7GVAh1_SU?si=9ARMZQnlu5FvkXJA

Have fun !
